  <prompt>
Verify FR-04 through FR-08: Documents, Matters, Projects, Invoices, Work Assignments row-click now opens Layout 1 (OOB modal at 85% × 85%) via the framework change from task 002.

No per-widget code change is needed — behavior change flows from the DataGrid `defaultRecordOpen` update. This task is verification-only, per-widget smoke test.

If ANY of the 5 widgets doesn't behave correctly, investigate and either (a) file a bug in task 002 or (b) document a per-widget exception via `onRecordOpen` prop override with rationale.
  </prompt>

  <role>QA engineer familiar with the SpaarkeAi workspace UI and Dataverse model-driven forms.</role>

  <goal>
Manual QA sign-off document `notes/phase1-verification.md` confirming: click a row in each of the 5 widgets → OOB modal opens at 85% × 85% showing the entity's default main form → Save & Close returns to workspace. Screenshots or Loom optional. Deviations documented per widget.
  </goal>

