  <steps>
    <step>Deploy the updated Spaarke.UI.Components + LegalWorkspace to the dev environment (build + code-page-deploy).</step>
    <step>Open LegalWorkspace / SpaarkeAi in dev, navigate to a workspace containing each widget.</step>
    <step>Documents widget: click a document row → verify OOB modal opens at 85%×85% showing Document main form.</step>
    <step>Matters widget: click a matter row → verify same behavior for Matter main form.</step>
    <step>Projects widget: click → verify Project main form.</step>
    <step>Invoices widget: click → verify Invoice main form.</step>
    <step>Work Assignments widget: click → verify Work Assignment main form.</step>
    <step>For each: verify ESC closes; Save & Close returns to workspace; no browser new-tab.</step>
    <step>Document results in `notes/phase1-verification.md` — one row per widget with pass/fail + notes.</step>
    <step>If any widget deviates, investigate root cause (config record misconfig? DataGrid regression?) — coordinate with task 002 if code fix needed.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>Bash · Read · Write · code-page-deploy skill · ui-test skill (optional)</tools>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion>All 5 widgets tested; results documented in `notes/phase1-verification.md`.</criterion>
    <criterion>Each widget opens OOB modal at 85%×85% (Layout 1); no new-tab behavior anywhere.</criterion>
    <criterion>ESC + Save & Close work correctly on each modal.</criterion>
    <criterion>Any deviations investigated with documented root cause (either fixed in task 002 or documented as Path A exception).</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
